Asian Tuna Salad 
(Serves 2)

Ingredients:
- 1 12 oz. can of light tuna in water.
- 3 green onions.
- 1 large or 2 small celery ribs.
- 5 whole water chestnuts.
- 1 oz. whole raw almonds (about 24)
- 1 tbsp. extra-virgin olive oil.
- 2 tbsp. rice vingar.
- 2 tbsp. soy sauce.
- 5-6 drops sesame oil.
- 1/2 tsp. sugar.


